Package: stance
Type: Package
Title: Continuous Bayesian Decoder for fMRI Analysis
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Your", "Name", email = "your.email@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
    )
Description: A Continuous Bayesian Decoder (CBD) for analyzing fMRI data using 
    variational Bayes inference. The package integrates seamlessly with 
    established R neuroimaging infrastructure (neuroim2, fmrireg) to provide 
    efficient spatial pattern learning and temporal state inference with 
    voxel-specific HRF estimation and spatial smoothing priors.
